{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"2f35e922-189d-4bd5-ba01-da30b1f8b7bc","content":"Use `dotnet watch test` with the `--filter` option:\n\n```bash\ndotnet watch test --filter \"FullyQualifiedName~ProcessPayment_NegativeAmount_ThrowsException\"\n```\n\nThis will:\n- **`dotnet watch test`** — re-run tests automatically on file save (hot reload)\n- **`--filter \"FullyQualifiedName~...\"`** — only run the matching test (`~` means \"contains\")\n\nYou can also filter by just the method name:\n\n```bash\ndotnet watch test --filter \"Name=ProcessPayment_NegativeAmount_ThrowsException\"\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5ac9b529-e583-4a8a-b81a-a9d3d0a0752d","outputTokens":151,"requestId":"A037:21B4FC:19AE957:1D30A0E:69FE9248"},"id":"d3f07e89-eb36-4a8e-8098-84f5562a9bfa","timestamp":"2026-05-09T01:47:56.591Z","parentId":"5e758bb4-1c3d-4d91-a8c3-d682ad31034e"}
